rge;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國</span>家重點實驗室</span></strong>的協助下，耗資約三十萬元，花一年時間製作。他指最初構思畢業論文題目時，計劃結合不同種類電燈的好處，研發出一款新型燈，對可為產品申請專利感到驚喜，未來希望將技術應用於製作光管。他指正與數間公司商討合作，每個新型燈泡預計售四十元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170309/photo/0309-00176-021h1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170309%2Fphoto%2F0309-00176-021h1.jpg&h=bfd47aa5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">趙崇智（左）指正與數間公司商討合作，每個新型燈泡預計售四十元。（高嘉業攝）</span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未讀過大學我唔怪你"},{"pid":"7902111de2ea626409d7a9ca1c22fef01e19421d","tid":149321,"uid":34771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:43:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>理大差唔多一個月就有新發明<br />\n但排名點解連屎大都比唔上？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新論文=/=新發明<br />\n<br />\napplication一定難過theory"},{"pid":"cf2d7d30135f29ffe86e47d22434f4561dfe9c03","tid":149321,"uid":32676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:53:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你話發明左一種發光油漆油上去天花板，完全取代電燈，唔駛用電，咁先好報出黎啦</blockquote><br />\nFirst law of thermodynamics<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f7f35d99beae471fd31317281265a8aa8369d66","tid":149321,"uid":61211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:56:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你話發明左一種發光油漆油上去天花板，完全取代電燈，唔駛用電，咁先好報出黎啦</blockquote><br />\n世上無哂你呢啲on9仔就要報啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/asset