><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國</span>家重點實驗室</span></strong>的協助下，耗資約三十萬元，花一年時間製作。他指最初構思畢業論文題目時，計劃結合不同種類電燈的好處，研發出一款新型燈，對可為產品申請專利感到驚喜，未來希望將技術應用於製作光管。他指正與數間公司商討合作，每個新型燈泡預計售四十元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170309/photo/0309-00176-021h1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170309%2Fphoto%2F0309-00176-021h1.jpg&h=bfd47aa5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">趙崇智（左）指正與數間公司商討合作，每個新型燈泡預計售四十元。（高嘉業攝）</span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未讀過大學我唔怪你</blockquote><br />\n一邊屌支共，一邊拎人錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bbc04234460ccb37a8ae73175ff32b7d37bc416","tid":149321,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T11:32:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用鋁基板, Led 做埋rectifier (half wave 25Hz)，muti chip in series,  如果得依啲特色，同現有LED 真係分別唔大，除非篇文個125瓦特即係125lm/W 意思，咁真係創新，不過CRI 又點？用窄光譜熒光LED 要做到&gt;120 lm/W 已經應用左好耐(&gt;10年)<br />\n<br />\n用人地新聞稿作新聞，真係好懶</blockquote><br />\n睇開新聞稿對科學新聞有多少抵抗力"},{"pid":"d6ffdde25be55f2e3520f867be29c81c84467db0","tid":149321,"uid":45925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T11:47:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用鋁基板, Led 做埋rectifier (half wave 25Hz)，muti chip in series,  如果得依啲特色，同現有LED 真係分別唔大，除非篇文個125瓦特即係125lm/W 意思，咁真係創新，不過CRI 又點？用窄光譜熒光LED 要做到&gt;120 lm/W 已經應用左好耐(&gt;10年)<br />\n<br />\n用人地新聞稿作新聞，真係好懶</blockquote><br />\n睇開新聞稿對科學新聞有多少抵抗力</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁就係香港d大學嘅新科技發明 ?<br />\n我當唐嚇一跳，然後就得啖笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a5c70b3de96014f5f761129f100c38e4e7fb035","tid":149321,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0